insect.coverage.analysis.jaba
Class JABACoverage

java.lang.Object
  insect.coverage.analysis.Analysis
      insect.coverage.analysis.jaba.JABACoverage
public class JABACoverage
extends Analysis

Provides coverage information regarding nodes and edges in a program graph. Coverage is determined by mapping information from the executions of an instrumented program to the particular graph type. This mapping is done using the JABAExecCoverage class.

Author:
Anil Chawla
